Package tradedatacorp.tools.jsonparser

Interface JSON_Item

All Known Subinterfaces:
JSON_Composite, JSON_CompositeArray, JSON_CompositeMap, JSON_Number
All Known Implementing Classes:
JSON_Array, JSON_Boolean, JSON_Decimal, JSON_Integer, JSON_Null, JSON_Object, JSON_String
public interface JSON_Item
Base interface for all JSON value types. Defines the type constants and methods to get the type and value of a JSON item.
